author: John Walters
description: With "World's Most Evil Invention," SNL and host Dwayne Johnson boldly strode into a very dark area.
title: SNL channels its early taboo-bashing days with "World's Most Evil Invention" skit

author: Dave Itzkoff
description: “S.N.L.” paid homage to itself by having Mr. Baldwin sing Leonard Cohen’s “Hallelujah.” The host, Dwayne Johnson, considered a presidential run with Tom Hanks.
title: On ‘Saturday Night Live,’ Alec Baldwin Sings a Swan Song for Trump
